    url: "https://osdr.nasa.gov"
    notes: "Source data: OSD-101 (RR-1 gastrocnemius), OSD-401 (RR-5 gastrocnemius), OSD-326 (RR-9 gastrocnemius), OSD-289 (MHU-1/MHU-2 thymus), OSD-244 (RR-6 thymus), OSD-421 (RR-9 thymus), OSD-238 (MHU-2 dorsal skin), OSD-239 (MHU-2 femoral skin), OSD-243 (RR-6 skin), OSD-254 (RR-7 skin, C57BL/6J subset), OSD-100 (RR-1 eye), OSD-194 (RR-3 eye), OSD-397 (eye)"

